title: #92Noon! Montage/JG/Birk&Siny/Bercich/PJ
description: Montage to celebrate a Vikings win, some Gophers with JG, Matt Birk & Dave Sinykin offer big opinions at the end of the first hour, then Pete Bercich joins for Vikings recap and some spicy Kirk conversation, PJ Fleck updates us on cancelled Gophers football games and the status of the program!
